link_preview_attachment.title: Why Market Cap Doesn‚Äôt Matter for XRP! üöÄ  Most people think XRP can‚Äôt reach $10,000 because of market cap‚Äîbut that‚Äôs a myth. Here‚Äôs why:  üîπ XRP is built for high-speed transactions, settling in 3-5 seconds. If XRP even handles 10% of that, daily settlements will be in the trillions, requiring a higher price per token for liquidity efficiency.  üîπ Circulating supply matters.
